<span id="Description"></span>
==Descrição== 

The [[Image:Draft_SelectGroup.svg|24px]] '''Draft SelectGroup''' command selects the contents of selected [[Std_Group|Std Groups]] or group-like [[BIM_Workbench|BIM]] objects. For selected non-group objects, the contents of the group they are in is selected.

<span id="Usage"></span>
==Utilização== 

# Select one or more objects that are inside groups, and/or select one or more groups.
# There are several ways to invoke the command:
#* [[Draft_Workbench|Draft]]: Press the {{Button|[[Image:Draft_SelectGroup.svg|16px]] [[Draft_SelectGroup|Select Group]]}} button.
#* Draft: Select the {{MenuCommand|Utilities → [[Image:Draft_SelectGroup.svg|16px]] Select Group}} option from the menu, or from the [[Tree_View|Tree View]] or [[3D_View|3D View]] context menu.
#* [[BIM_Workbench|BIM]]: Select the {{MenuCommand|Utils → [[Image:Draft_SelectGroup.svg|16px]] Select Group}} option from the menu.
# The contents of the groups is selected.

==Notes==

* For more information about organizing your model see [[Document_structure|Document structure]] and [[Arch_tutorial#Organizing_your_model|Arch tutorial]].


